{"id":"blow","term":"Blow","source":"International Standard Bible Encyclopaedia (James Orr ed., 1915)","html":"<p>blo (nashaph): Used with reference to the wind (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 15:10\">Ex 15:10</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 78:26\">Ps 78:26</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 147:18\">147:18</a>; pneo, \"to breathe,\" <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 12:55\">Lu 12:55</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"John 3:8\">Joh 3:8</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Revelation 7:1\">Re 7:1</a>); taqa`, with reference to trumpet sound (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 10:3\">Nu 10:3-10</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 31:6\">31:6</a> the King James Version; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Judges 7:18\">Jud 7:18</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Revelation 7:3\">20</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 1:34\">1Ki 1:34</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 15:24\">1Ch 15:24</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 81:3\">Ps 81:3</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezekiel 33:3\">Eze 33:3</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezekiel 33:6\">6</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Hosea 5:8\">Ho 5:8</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Joel 2:1\">Joe 2:1</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Joel 2:15\">15</a>); puach, with reference to the strong expulsion of the breath (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezekiel 21:31\">Eze 21:31</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezekiel 22:20\">22:20</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezekiel 22:21\">21</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Haggai 1:9\">Hag 1:9</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 40:7\">Isa 40:7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 54:16\">54:16</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Job 20:26\">Job 20:26</a>); nashaph, with reference to a forcible slap or stroke with hand or an instrument (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 39:10\">Ps 39:10</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 40:24\">Isa 40:24</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Jeremiah 14:17\">Jer 14:17</a> the King James Version).</p><p>Frank E. Hirsch</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Exodus 15:10","Psalms 78:26","Psalms 147:18","Luke 12:55","John 3:8","Revelation 7:1","Numbers 10:3","Numbers 31:6","Judges 7:18","Revelation 7:3","1 Kings 1:34","1 Chronicles 15:24","Psalms 81:3","Ezekiel 33:3","Ezekiel 33:6","Hosea 5:8","Joel 2:1","Joel 2:15","Ezekiel 21:31","Ezekiel 22:20","Ezekiel 22:21","Haggai 1:9","Isaiah 40:7","Isaiah 54:16","Job 20:26","Psalms 39:10","Isaiah 40:24","Jeremiah 14:17"]}